stylometry: Decision thoery is anaylzing given data to make the best decision possible. This could be minimizing cost, maximizing profit, or trying to find the most efficient way to do something.  The payoff table shows the likelyhood of an outcome happening and the effect it would have. We use these components to find the best solution with the highest likelyhood of happening. This therefore allows the person to make the best decision possible with the information available.
